hanako:
**`/hanako`** Information about Hanako Ikezawa, the best grill

**Usage**: /hanako
help:
**`/help`** List of commands or information about a given command

**Usage**: /help [command]

**Examples**:
`/help`  List of commands
`/help ping`  Usage of the `ping` command
invite:
**`/invite`** Get a link to invite Natsuki to your server

**Usage**: /invite
vote:
**`/vote`** Natsuki on the Discord Bot List

**Usage**: /vote
This command just shows Natsuki's page on the Discord Bot List.  To vote, you have to follow the link and log in there.
cupcake:
**`/cupcake`** Bake cupcake out of someone

**Usage**: /cupcake [user]

The source of the cupcake is https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Hostess-Cupcake-Whole.jpg
poem:
**`/poem`** Play a poem game

**Usage**: /poem [act]

**Examples**:
`/poem 2`  Act 2 poem game
shelf:
**`/shelf`** Help Natsuki access the book on the shelf

**Usage**: /shelf [user]
ship:
**`/ship`** Ship specified characters

**Usage**: /ship [characters]
Every unescaped & is replaced with a √ó.

**Examples**:
`/ship`  Shipping you and Natsuki
`/ship [text without &]`  Shipping you and the text
`/ship [text] & [text]...`  Shipping ampersand-separated text
word:

**Example**:
`n.word` The n-word
`@Natsuki word` List of Natsuki's preferred words
neko:
